            Business Information
        






                    C+
                


                BBB Rating Scorecard
            










Pattern of Complaint

A recent review of BBB complaints has delineated a pattern of consumer allegations against Stericycle, Inc. In their complaints, consumers allege the following: - Continuous increase in fees without notice to businesses, which are then left unexplained by Stericycle. - Businesses want to cancel contracts, however, Stericycle charges exorbitant penalties to do so, which cannot be paid due to lack of funds ($1,000-$25,000). - Aggressive sales tacti...                                Read More














