Discover Stericycle
At Stericycle, we help businesses protect people and brands, promote health, and safeguard the environment. We provide an array of specialized solutions to healthcare organizations and businesses of all sizes. Watch the videos below to learn more about our company and what we do.





Environmental Solutions
At Stericycle, our highly train teams provide customers with a wide range of services designed to ensure compliance with environmental and waste regulations. We also maintain a large national network of specialized treatment, storage and disposal facilities.





Expert Solutions
At Stericycle, our teams mobilize resources quickly to address and stabilize difficult situations. Our ExpertSOLUTIONS team has worked with thousands of customers, larher and small across a wide range of industries to protect and enhance their brands.





Communication Solutions
At Stericycle, our friendly, knowledgeable team supports both healthcare and commercial organizations. We help our customers stay connected with their customers and patients in ways that build measurable, meaningful and profitable relationships.








