Working at Shred-it





In October of 2015, Stericycle acquired Shred-it International and added the complementary service of secure information destruction to our portfolio of business services.  Shred-It shares the entrepreneurial spirit and culture that makes Stericycle a great place to work.  In addition to jobs posted on this Stericycle careers site, please review career opportunities within our Shred-It organization.







